text: Stathmodera wagneri is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Adlbauer in 2006. It is known from Kenya.BioLib.cz - Stathmodera wagneri. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Apomecynini Category:Beetles described in 2006
